errors.name: InvalidSecp256r1VerifyArg
errors.msg: Malformed or missing WebAuthn verification parameters. Please provide valid secp256r1 signature arguments.

errors.name: InvalidSecp256r1Instruction
errors.msg: The instruction preceding this program invocation is not a secp256r1 verification instruction.

errors.name: SignatureIndexOutOfBounds
errors.msg: The signature index provided is out of bounds for the secp256r1 instruction.

errors.name: InvalidSignatureOffsets
errors.msg: Failed to deserialize secp256r1 signature offsets from the instruction data.

errors.name: InvalidSecp256r1PublicKey
errors.msg: The extracted public key has an invalid length or encoding.

errors.name: MalformedSignedMessage
errors.msg: The extracted WebAuthn signed message payload is malformed.

errors.name: RpIdHashMismatch
errors.msg: The rpIdHash extracted from the signed message does not match the expected value.

errors.name: ClientDataHashMismatch
errors.msg: The clientDataJSON hash extracted from the signature does not match the generated hash.

errors.name: ExpectedMessageHashMismatch
errors.msg: The message hash associated with the signer does not match the pre-declared expected message hash.

errors.name: DurableNonceDetected
errors.msg: Durable nonce detected: this program does not support transactions using a durable nonce.

errors.name: DuplicateMember
errors.msg: Duplicate public keys detected among members. Each member must have a unique key.

errors.name: PermanentMember
errors.msg: Permanent members cannot be removed from a wallet.

errors.name: OnlyOnePermanentMemberAllowed
errors.msg: Only one permanent member is allowed per wallet.

errors.name: InvalidPermanentMemberConfig
errors.msg: User with Permanent Member role must have a delegated wallet.

errors.name: OnlyOneTransactionManagerAllowed
errors.msg: Only one transaction manager is allowed per wallet.

errors.name: InvalidTransactionManagerPermission
errors.msg: Invalid Transaction Manager permissions. Only initiate is allowed.

errors.name: ExpectedTransactionManagerRoleMismatch
errors.msg: Expected a User with Transaction Manager role for this instruction.

errors.name: InvalidTransactionManagerConfig
errors.msg: User with Transaction Manager role requires a valid transaction manager url, be a ed25519 Signer and have no delegated wallet.

errors.name: ExpectedAdministratorRoleMismatch
errors.msg: Expected a User with Administrator role for this instruction.

errors.name: InvalidAdministratorConfig
errors.msg: User with Administrator role requires a valid domain config, be a ed25519 Signer and have no delegated wallet.

errors.name: EmptyMembers
errors.msg: No members provided. A multisig wallet must contain at least one member.

errors.name: TooManyMembers
errors.msg: Too many members: a maximum of 4 members are supported.

errors.name: InvalidThreshold
errors.msg: Invalid threshold: must be at least 1 and cannot exceed the number of voting-eligible members.

errors.name: InvalidTransactionMessage
errors.msg: Malformed transaction message: structure or formatting does not match the expected layout.

errors.name: InvalidNumberOfAccounts
errors.msg: Unexpected number of accounts provided for this instruction.

errors.name: InvalidAccount
errors.msg: One or more provided accounts failed validation. Verify that all required accounts are included and correct.

errors.name: InvalidUserRole
errors.msg: One or more provided user accounts failed validation. Verify that only users with appropriate roles are allowed to perform this action.

errors.name: InvalidArguments
errors.msg: Invalid or missing instruction arguments. Ensure all required arguments are correctly provided.

errors.name: MissingAccount
errors.msg: A required account is missing from the instruction context.

errors.name: MissingMutationUserArgs
errors.msg: User mutation arguments are required when performing add or remove delegate operations.

errors.name: AlreadyDelegated
errors.msg: This member is already delegated to another wallet.

errors.name: InsufficientSignerWithExecutePermission
errors.msg: At least one signer with execute permission is required to proceed.

errors.name: InsufficientSignerWithInitiatePermission
errors.msg: At least one signer with initiate permission is required to perform this action.

errors.name: InsufficientSignersWithVotePermission
errors.msg: Not enough members with vote permission to meet the approval threshold.

errors.name: InvalidNonDelegatedSigners
errors.msg: Only delegated members are allowed for this transaction.

errors.name: UnexpectedSigner
errors.msg: Member is not part of the expected signers for this transaction.

errors.name: NoSignerFound
errors.msg: No valid signer found in this transaction.

errors.name: UnauthorisedToCloseTransactionBuffer
errors.msg: Only the transaction creator or rent payer may close this transaction buffer.

errors.name: InvalidBuffer
errors.msg: Buffer validation failed: contents do not match the expected hash (possible tampering detected).

errors.name: FinalBufferHashMismatch
errors.msg: Final buffer hash mismatch: the serialized data may be corrupted or altered.

errors.name: FinalBufferSizeExceeded
errors.msg: The serialized transaction buffer exceeds the maximum size of 10,128 bytes.

errors.name: FinalBufferSizeMismatch
errors.msg: Declared buffer size does not match the actual serialized size.

errors.name: TransactionHasExpired
errors.msg: This transaction has expired. It must be executed within 3 minutes of approval.

errors.name: TransactionNotApproved
errors.msg: This transaction has not yet reached the required approval threshold.

errors.name: ProtectedAccount
errors.msg: Writable CPI calls to protected accounts are not permitted.

errors.name: MaxLengthExceeded
errors.msg: An input string exceeds the maximum allowed character length.

errors.name: MissingSysvarSlotHistory
errors.msg: Missing required sysvar: Slot History must be included as an account in this instruction.

errors.name: InvalidSysvarDataFormat
errors.msg: Failed to parse the Slot History sysvar: data format is invalid or corrupted.

errors.name: SlotNumberNotFound
errors.msg: The specified slot number was not found in the provided slot history.

errors.name: InvalidSlotNumber
errors.msg: The specified slot number is not recent enough. Slot must be within the recent slot history window.

errors.name: DomainConfigIsDisabled
errors.msg: The domain configuration account is disabled. Please contact support or try again later.

errors.name: DomainConfigIsMissing
errors.msg: Missing domain configuration account.

errors.name: MemberDoesNotBelongToDomainConfig
errors.msg: This member is not registered under the provided domain configuration.

errors.name: OriginIndexOutOfBounds
errors.msg: The given origin index is not in the whitelisted origins.

errors.name: InvalidAddressTree
errors.msg: Address Tree supplied is not part of the whitelisted address trees.

errors.name: MissingSettingsData
errors.msg: Compressed settings data is missing. The settings account must be initialized with data.

errors.name: HashComputationFailed
errors.msg: Failed to compute hash. This may indicate a system error.

errors.name: EmptySlotNumbers
errors.msg: Slot numbers list is empty. At least one slot number is required for validation.

errors.name: InvalidMemberKeyFormat
errors.msg: Member key conversion failed. The provided key format is invalid.

errors.name: MissingCompressedProofArgs
errors.msg: Compressed proof arguments are missing. Required for compressed account operations.

errors.name: MissingLightCpiAccounts
errors.msg: Light CPI accounts are missing. Required for compressed account operations.

errors.name: MemberNotFound
errors.msg: Member not found in settings. Cannot remove a member that does not exist.

errors.name: SettingsKeyMismatch
errors.msg: Settings key mismatch. The provided settings key does not match the expected value.

errors.name: PayerMismatch
errors.msg: Payer account mismatch. The provided payer does not match the transaction buffer payer.

errors.name: MissingCompressedTokenAccount
errors.msg: Missing compressed token account. Required for token transfer operations.

errors.name: MissingSplInterfacePda
errors.msg: Missing SPL interface PDA. Required for token transfer operations.

errors.name: MissingInstructionsSysvar
errors.msg: Missing instructions sysvar account. Required for secp256r1 signature verification.

errors.name: LightCpiAccountError
errors.msg: Light CPI account operation failed. The account may be invalid or uninitialized.

errors.name: InvalidTokenSourceType
errors.msg: Invalid source type for token transfer. The source account type is not supported.

errors.name: SourceAccountMismatch
errors.msg: Source account mismatch. The provided source account does not match the expected wallet vault address.

errors.name: MemberNotFoundInSettings
errors.msg: Member not found in settings members list. Cannot update delegate flag for a non-existent member.

errors.name: InvalidAccountIndex
errors.msg: Invalid account index in transaction message. The account index is out of bounds.

errors.name: DomainConfigKeyMismatch
errors.msg: Domain configuration account key mismatch. The provided domain config does not match the expected value.

errors.name: MissingUserAccountAddress
errors.msg: User account address is missing. Required for secp256r1 signature verification.

errors.name: ClockSysvarAccessFailed
errors.msg: Clock sysvar access failed. This may indicate a system error.

errors.name: UnauthorizedAdminOnly
errors.msg: Unauthorized: Only the admin account is allowed to perform this action.

errors.name: InvalidUserTransactionManagerConfig
errors.msg: Invalid user configuration. Transaction manager URL must be empty for non-transaction-manager users.

errors.name: MissingDestinationTokenAccount
errors.msg: Missing destination token account. Required for token transfer operations.

errors.name: MissingSourceTokenAccount
errors.msg: Missing source token account. Required for token transfer operations.

errors.name: MissingSettingsAccountForDelegate
errors.msg: Missing settings account. Required for delegate operations on compressed wallets.

errors.name: MissingNewAuthority
errors.msg: Missing new authority account. Required for domain configuration updates.

errors.name: MissingWhitelistedAddressTrees
errors.msg: Missing whitelisted address trees account. Required for domain configuration updates.

errors.name: DuplicateAddressTree
errors.msg: Duplicate address tree detected. This address tree is already in the whitelist.

types.name: CompressedOnlyExtension
docs: CompressedOnly extension for compressed token accounts.
This extension marks a compressed account as decompress-only (cannot be transferred).
It stores the delegated amount from the source Token account when it was compressed-and-closed.

fields.name: delegated_amount
docs: The delegated amount from the source Token account's delegate field.
When decompressing, the decompression amount must match this value.

fields.name: withheld_transfer_fee
docs: Withheld transfer fee amount from the source Token account.

fields.name: is_ata
docs: Whether the source was an ATA (1) or regular token account (0).
When is_ata=1, decompress must verify ATA derivation matches.

types.name: CompressibleExtension
docs: Compressible extension for token accounts.
This extension contains compression configuration and timing data.

fields.name: decimals_option
docs: Option discriminator for decimals (0 = None, 1 = Some)

fields.name: decimals
docs: Token decimals (only valid when decimals_option == 1)

fields.name: compression_only
docs: Whether this account is compression-only (cannot decompress)

fields.name: is_ata
docs: Whether the source account is an ATA (1 = ATA, 0 = regular account)
Used during compress_and_close to set is_ata in CompressedOnlyExtension

fields.name: info
docs: Compression configuration and timing data

types.name: CompressionInfo
docs: Compressible extension for ctoken accounts.

fields.name: compress_to_pubkey
docs: Compress to account pubkey instead of account owner.

fields.name: account_version
docs: Version of the compressed token account when ctoken account is
compressed and closed. (The account_version specifies the hashing scheme.)

fields.name: lamports_per_write
docs: Lamports amount the account is topped up with at every write
by the fee payer.

fields.name: compression_authority
docs: Authority that can compress and close the account.

fields.name: rent_sponsor
docs: Recipient for rent exemption lamports up on account closure.

fields.name: last_claimed_slot
docs: Last slot rent was claimed from this account.

fields.name: rent_exemption_paid
docs: Rent exemption lamports paid at account creation.
Used instead of querying the Rent sysvar to ensure rent sponsor
gets back exactly what they paid regardless of future rent changes.

fields.name: _reserved
docs: Reserved for future use.

fields.name: rent_config
docs: Rent function parameters,
used to calculate whether the account is compressible.

types.name: PausableAccountExtension
docs: Marker extension indicating the account belongs to a pausable mint.
This is a zero-size marker (no data) that indicates the token account's
mint has the SPL Token 2022 Pausable extension.
When present, token operations must check the SPL mint's PausableConfig
to determine if the mint is paused before allowing transfers.

types.name: PermanentDelegateAccountExtension
docs: Marker extension indicating the account belongs to a mint with permanent delegate.
This is a zero-size marker (no data) that indicates the token account's
mint has the SPL Token 2022 Permanent Delegate extension.
When present, token operations must check the SPL mint's PermanentDelegate
to determine the delegate authority before allowing transfers/burns.

types.name: Permissions
docs: Bitmask for permissions.

types.name: RentConfig
docs: Rent function parameters,
used to calculate whether the account is compressible.

fields.name: base_rent
docs: Base rent constant: rent = base_rent + num_bytes * lamports_per_byte_per_epoch

fields.name: max_top_up
docs: Maximum lamports that can be charged per top-up operation.
Protects against griefing by accounts with high lamports_per_write.

types.name: TokenMetadata
docs: Used for onchain serialization

fields.name: update_authority
docs: The authority that can sign to update the metadata
None if zero

fields.name: mint
docs: The associated mint, used to counter spoofing to be sure that metadata
belongs to a particular mint

fields.name: name
docs: The longer name of the token

fields.name: symbol
docs: The shortened symbol for the token

fields.name: uri
docs: The URI pointing to richer metadata

fields.name: additional_metadata
docs: Any additional metadata about the token as key-value pairs. The program
must avoid storing the same key twice.

fields.name: multi_wallet_settings
docs: The multisig settings this belongs to.

fields.name: multi_wallet_bump
docs: The bump for the multi_wallet

fields.name: can_execute
docs: Flag to allow transaction to be executed

fields.name: preauthorize_execution
docs: Flag to preauthorize execution before sufficient threshold is met

fields.name: payer
docs: Payer for the transaction buffer

fields.name: bump
docs: transaction bump

fields.name: buffer_index
docs: Index to seed address derivation

fields.name: final_buffer_hash
docs: Hash of the final assembled transaction message.

fields.name: final_buffer_size
docs: The size of the final assembled transaction message.

fields.name: creator
docs: Member of the Multisig who created the TransactionBuffer.

fields.name: executor
docs: Member of the Multisig who executed the TransactionBuffer.

fields.name: buffer_extend_hashes
docs: Buffer hash for all the buffer extend instruction

fields.name: voters
docs: Members that voted for this transaction

fields.name: expected_secp256r1_signers
docs: All Secp256r1 Signers that are expected to initiate / vote / execute this transaction (used for off-chain inspection by the transaction manager)

fields.name: buffer
docs: The buffer of the transaction message.

types.name: TransferFeeAccountExtension
docs: Transfer fee extension for Token accounts.
Stores withheld fees that accumulate during transfers.
Mirrors SPL Token-2022's TransferFeeAmount extension.

fields.name: withheld_amount
docs: Amount withheld during transfers, to be harvested on decompress

types.name: TransferHookAccountExtension
docs: Extension indicating the account belongs to a mint with transfer hook.
Contains a `transferring` flag used as a reentrancy guard during hook CPI.
Consistent with SPL Token-2022 TransferHookAccount layout.

fields.name: transferring
docs: Flag to indicate that the account is in the middle of a transfer.
Used as reentrancy guard when transfer hook program is called via CPI.
Always false at rest since we only support nil program_id (no hook invoked).
